OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeruvian ex-minister       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcomplicit in reporter's    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmurder                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Peruvian ex-interior minister was    
OL,6, complicit in the 1988 killing of Hugo  
OL,7, Bustios, a journalist who investigated 
OL,8, human rights abuses, a court has found.
OL,10,FThe former minister, Daniel Urresti,   
OL,11,Fhas been sentenced to 12 years in jail.
OL,13,FThe court ruled that Urresti, who at   
OL,14,Fthe time was a military intelligence   
OL,15,Fofficer in the army, took part in the  
OL,16,Fambush and murder of Mr Bustios.       
OL,18,FLawyers for the politician said they   
OL,19,Fwould appeal against the verdict.      
